The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a khaki green and black color scheme. Who he was doesn't change who he has become. Don't worry Felix... The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. It has been painted with a pattern of nuclear hazard symbols using metallic paints.
